{"type": "article", "id": 28866, "title": "像照片一样的音响", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-29T06:59:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703121804VxwichfpoRnjQSKY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>可以听的照片不再是天方夜谭了：当你第一眼看到 Touch of Bass 系列并且听到音乐时可能还会纳闷音源来自何方。实际上，这些由 <a href=\"http://www.caseofbass.com/\">Case of Bass</a> 设计的产品本身就是一个精致的音响设备。机身隐藏在相片背后的暗盒中，真实的喇叭则穿过相片中预留的空缺处，最外面则是固定用的相框——远远看上去就是一幅栩栩如生的摄影作品，只有靠近了从侧面观察才能惊喜地发现那些隐藏的细节。Touch of Bass 的高颜值和实用性让它不管放置在什么环境下都会让人眼前一亮，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/368403916/a-touch-of-bass-the-sound-system-for-the-aesthetic\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121801btYOmU0GPxNeZT9B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312180157EcgqGRQkVw19oT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121802gNdCH3DKs7xZbphT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703121802BTJwMhebk6mtcxzS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63043478\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}